trans-unit.source: Specifies the type of print operation occurring.
trans-unit.target: 指定列印作業發生型的別。

trans-unit.source: The PrintAction is used by the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintEventArgs> type to indicate what type of <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.Print%2A> event is occurring.
trans-unit.target: 使用 PrintAction<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintEventArgs>型別以表示何種<xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.Print%2A>發生事件。</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintDocument.Print%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintEventArgs>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The <xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintEventArgs.PrintAction%2A?displayProperty=fullName> does not reliably indicate the type of print operation occurring, and returns PrintToFile in all cases.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] ><xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintEventArgs.PrintAction%2A?displayProperty=fullName>不可靠地表示的列印作業發生的型別，並在所有情況下傳回 PrintToFile。</xref:System.Drawing.Printing.PrintEventArgs.PrintAction%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The print operation is printing to a file.
trans-unit.target: 列印作業正在列印至檔案。

trans-unit.source: The print operation is a print preview.
The print operation is printing to a printer.
trans-unit.target: 列印作業正在列印至印表機。
